### 1. GET ALL BLOGS
# Fetches all blogs from the database (should include the seeded data).
GET http://localhost:3002/api/blogs

### 2. POST A NEW BLOG (Create)
# Creates a new blog post. Note the 'title' and 'url' fields are required.
POST http://localhost:3002/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Blog Post No 1. Posted from REST Client",
    "author": "VS Code REST Client",
    "url": "http:/VS-Code/rest-client",
    "likes": 41
}

### 3. POST ANOTHER BLOG (To easily get an ID for deletion testing)
